Le Méridien Piccadilly is a luxury 5-star hotel in London, England. The rooms are divided into sets by type including Classic Rooms, Deluxe Rooms, Club Rooms and Executive Junior Suites.

The hotel was constructed in 1908 as The Piccadilly Hotel and passed through numerous owners, before being bought by Le Méridien in 1986.
Le Méridien Piccadilly was bought by American company Host Hotels & Resorts in 2010 after a £6 million refurbishment.


